"<h4>Templating</h4>\n\n"
"<p>Templates are compiled using the Jinja Templating Language. To learn more about Jinja, <a class=\"strong\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/dev/templates/\">read this documentation.</a></p>"
